ies are different than in\nmore typical, higher surface brightness spiral galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Jun 2005 23:56:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Jun 2005 17:22:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
